name: Escape from Space-Astronaut 64
description:
This is about the game named "Escape From the Space-Astronaut-64". In it, you will have to escape from the spaceship and avoid the alien enemies. This game is created by Kaung Htet Kyaw and It has 4 levels named

  • Level 1
  • Level 2
  • Level 3
  • Level 4

If you want to enjoy more, please play the game......
